title: Ep. 75 Millennials In Quarantine w/ Chase O'Donnell - Where My Moms At w/ Christina P
description:
SPONSORS: - Discover the New Michelin® CrossClimate® 2 tires at https://MichelinMan.com - To work your magic with OxiClean, go to https://OxiClean.com/tryme and order a free sample - Go to https://MagicSpoon.com/WMMA and use code WMMA at checkout to get free shipping. - Go to https://AdamAndEve.com and use code WMMA to get 50% off plus 10 free gifts! - Go to https://HelloFresh.com/80wmma and use code 80wmma to get $80 off including free shipping! - Go to https://SkylightFrame.com and use code CHRISTINA to get $10 off your purchase of a Skylight Frame - Go to https://Ancestry.com/WMMA to get your Ancestry gift today

WHERE MY MOMS AT!? It's the show by the Moms for the Moms. Hosted by everybody's favorite "cool mom" Christina P! Not only the most REAL show for moms, but the most interactive. An open place to admit no one really knows what they're doing.

In the midst of all these crazy times, we need to check in with our resident millennial comedian Chase O'Donnell to see what the kids are up to! What are they drinking? What are they watching? What are they listening to? Christina P gets all the info moms and dads need to stay hip and cool during these trying times!

Christina P. wants to hear from you since she is seriously lacking in cool mom friends. If you want to share a "Mom Fail" or "Mom Hack" please call into our voicemail (213)375-5184 and let Christina know! We want to talk to as many moms across America as we can.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
